    Interface and Description
    org.threadly.concurrent.CallableContainerInterface
    Please use CallableContainer
    org.threadly.util.ExceptionHandlerInterface
    Please use ExceptionHandler

  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.threadly.concurrent.limiter.PrioritySchedulerLimiter
    Mixing priorities does not make sense, wrap a priority scheduler with a PrioritySchedulerWrapper and use SubmitterSchedulerLimiter to limit within a given priority
    org.threadly.concurrent.PrioritySchedulerWrapper
    Use PrioritySchedulerDefaultPriorityWrapper as a direct replacement
    org.threadly.concurrent.limiter.SimpleSchedulerLimiter
    Use SubmitterSchedulerLimiter
    org.threadly.test.concurrent.TestablePriorityScheduler
    Use TestableScheduler now that it also implements PrioritySchedulerInterface
